	<h1 class="title">布鲁塞尔全城戒严，整个欧洲的安全都面临威胁</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Alissa J. Rubin, Aurelien Breeden and Anita Raghavan</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-23 15:38:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/24326/medium/24326.jpg?1458714746" alt="" />			
	</div>
